Peruvian President Ollanta Humala
signed into effect a law creating a mining windfall tax that
will finance increased public spending.  The tax on profits will help create jobs and finance
infrastructure investment such as hospitals, Humala said today
at the signing ceremony at the Presidential Palace. Peru is the
